@baseUrl = http://localhost:5100

### Check that the API is running
GET {{baseUrl}}/

### OpenAPI document
GET {{baseUrl}}/openapi/v1.json

### Get all events
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/events

### Filter by city
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/events?city=Munich

### Get event details with sessions and speakers
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/events/1

### Get sessions for one event
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/events/1/sessions

### Create a valid event
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/events
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Debugging Distributed Systems",
  "date": "2026-08-12T09:00:00",
  "city": "Salzburg",
  "description": "A focused workshop on diagnosing production issues."
}

### Create an invalid event (built-in validation + FluentValidation)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/events
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "",
  "date": "2020-01-01T09:00:00",
  "city": "X",
  "description": "This should fail validation."
}

### Update an event
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/events/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "TechConf Architecture Day - Updated",
  "date": "2026-06-19T09:00:00",
  "city": "Munich",
  "description": "Updated after finalizing the agenda."
}

### Trigger a 404 ProblemDetails response
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/events/999

### Trigger a 500 ProblemDetails response
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/debug/fail
